public interface Constants

ANIMAL

static final byte ANIMAL
Animal representation --> used mainly to be bitwised to check the availability of the next movement. e.g. Animal 12 = 1100, Rabbit 14 = 1110, Fox 15 = 1111; contains the first tow bits alike to distinguish them from other data
